               <decoDesc>
                  <decoNote type="overview">Decoration in neobyzantine style with interlacing
                     elements. </decoNote>
                  <decoNote type="borders">
                     <locus>F.1</locus> little red border with "pletenie", in an unfinished
                     state; <locus>f.158</locus> : big quadratic border, with round medalions inside,with floral
                     elements, in blu and gold (in very poor condition); <locus>f. 310</locus> and <locus>311</locus>: simple
                     "pletenie" in red and blu. </decoNote>
                  <decoNote type="initials">
                     <locus>F.4</locus> and <locus>f.158</locus> : big ornamented initials in red and
